    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
      <p>This collection consists of correspondence letters,
         business and legal papers of the Rives Family. Correspondents
         include Alexander Brown, James P. Henderson, Samuel Pannill,
         Alexander Rives, Cornelia Rives, Elizabeth Pannill Rives,
         Margaret Cabell Rives, Robert Rives, Jr., William Cabell
         Rives,</p>
    </scopecontent>
